      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Etcd作为配置源头。那Redis缓存是单层还是多层？我注意到您提到了\"几层\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，设计上是两层Redis。第一层直接连Etcd做配置同步，第二层再连到Worker节点。这样B节点连C节点，C节点再往下走。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出这条主干：A是Etcd集群，B和C是两层Redis，D是Worker节点。A到B，B到C，C到D。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
