        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Worker节点之后有个关键循环逻辑——每次代码提交迁移时，要走一个子流程。里面涉及Ingress控制器和Redis的交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这个循环是子图的形式吗？我可以用subgraph包起来，标注\"LOOP FOR EACH COMMIT TO MOVE\"。里面具体几个节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_IngressController",
